---
inputs:
  usfm_refs: "Reference data with USFM codes"
outputs:
  greek_texts: "Batch MCP response"
---

Fetch ALL these biblical references in ONE batch call.

References to fetch: {{usfm_refs.usfm_batch}}

Make EXACTLY ONE call to `get_passage_text`:
```json
{
  "usfm_references": {{usfm_refs.usfm_batch}},
  "textual_editions": ["SBLGNT"]
}
```

Return the MCP response as JSON:
```json
{
  "batch_response": <MCP response>,
  "num_fetched": <number>
}
```